        "heading_level": "h2",
        "body": "<p>Our campaign takes a joyful look at what we share. Shot in one take, this high-energy film celebrates the intuition, recognition, and magnetism between women—as seen through the implicit knowing and unexpected mirroring of two models who've never met before: <strong>Tina Kunakey</strong> and <strong>Caroline Kelley Rosen</strong>. As they draw us into the rhythms of interconnection, we realize we are all more alike than we imagine.</p>",
